headline: Match Group’s rape problem: A lawsuit alleges that inaction by Tinder and Hinge’s owner allowed abusers to stay on the apps
summary: A shareholder alleges the company "has known… which users have been reported for drugging, assaulting, or raping their dates since at least 2016" but did not release a promised report.
